<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hen" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hen,</orth> the female of the cock: <bibl n="shak. shr 2.227" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 227</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 1, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.162" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 3, 162</bibl>. a female pigeon: <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.151" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 151</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.108" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 108</bibl>. a female pheasant: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.771" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 771</bibl>. term of contempt, to denote cowardice: <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.224" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 3, 224</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>